Cuke4AS3 Developer allows ActionScript to be used for Cucumber step definitions

Wiki Home:
https://github.com/flashquartermaster/Cuke4AS3/wiki

How to use Cuke4AS3 Developer UI:
https://github.com/flashquartermaster/Cuke4AS3/wiki/How-To-Use-Cuke4AS3

Please note you do not have to use the Developer UI but it can be helpful if you area starting out or as a primer. 
Cuke4AS3 is actually a library that you can implement your own UI over if you so wish or run in server only mode to 
sit alongside Cucumber:
https://github.com/flashquartermaster/Cuke4AS3/blob/master/Cuke4AS3/README
https://github.com/flashquartermaster/Cuke4AS3/blob/master/Cuke4AS3/test/features/cuke4as3/server-only.feature
https://github.com/flashquartermaster/Cuke4AS3/blob/master/Cuke4AS3/test/features/step_definitions/ServerOnly_Steps.as

Important info on how to work with the source code:
https://github.com/flashquartermaster/Cuke4AS3/wiki/Working-With-The-Source

Cuke4AS3 Documentation:

Relish
https://www.relishapp.com/flashquartermaster/cuke4as3/

Cuke4AS3Lib
http://flashquartermaster.com/cuke4as3/lib/docs/

Cuke4AS3
http://flashquartermaster.com/cuke4as3/core/docs/

Please Note:
No contributions will be accepted unless they have accompanying unit tests and where necessary features and step definitions